'       SSSS     EEEEEE     RRRRRRRR   VVV   VVV   III   DDD   DDD  OOO   OOO  RRRRRRRR
'          SSS   EEE        RRR RRR     VVV VVV    III   DDD   DDD  OOO   OOO  RRR RRR
'     SSS   SSS  EEE        RRR  RRR     VVVVV     III   DDD   DDD  OOO   OOO  RRR  RRR
